headline: Could Buying Costco Today Set You Up for Life?
summary: Costco (NASDAQ: COST) is a store I frequent almost weekly, thanks to the good prices and the shockingly fresh produce.  Would adding Costco to your portfolio right now set you up for a lifetime of strong returns?  The first thing that investors have to get their heads around when it comes to Costco is the business.

headline: Largest U.S. Pension Sold GE Aerospace and Tesla Stock, Bought AT&T and Costco
